text: Just had the mee pok dry and added $1.50 meatball. The noodle is a little too soft for my liking but acceptable. Taste wise, it is quite nice. The ingredients are fresh and tasty. Soup is clear but yummy.

Visited on 21 Apr 2024 for lunch after cycling. The meepok is nice with umami taste and the soup ingredient is not too salty and with mellow aroma of fishball, minced pork, pork slices, and yanjiao üòã
This place eats regularly, it's delicious, and it has a lot of meals.

The Vietnamese girl is v hardworking... She's well mannered... She even concerned of slow in sales ... Immpecabble worker.
